long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension provides safe search suggestions directly in the address bar to filter out unsafe content, ensuring a secure online environment. The default search is powered by Yahoo.

Learn more - https://safe.kidsmode.site/
